section.p:
The start process for case details must be implemented and it must accept caseId parameter to pass the case id.
				Using code block to add start link href of case details page to case object with this key "CASE_DETAIL_PROCESS" 


				param : Number caseId


	     		for example :


	     		import ch.ivy.addon.portalkit.util.CaseUtils;

				ivy.case.setAdditionalProperty(CaseUtils.CASE_DETAIL_PROCESS, ivy.html.startref("14BDECA22347DEF2/OpenCaseDetails.ivp"));
				result :
	     		http://localhost:8081/ivy/pro/designer/test001InternalSupport/14C7986FD23D7C89/caseDetails.ivp?caseId=317
